sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant N as nginx (TLS terminator)
    participant S as MTProxy server

    C->>N: TLS ClientHello
    N-->>C: TLS ServerHello
    C->>N: HTTP GET /ws (Upgrade: websocket)
    N-->>C: 101 Switching Protocols
    C->>S: (proxied) WS frame: Session Header
    S-->>C: WS frame: MTProto ack
    Note over C,S: Obfuscated-2 payload from here on
